<h1>Rental Car Pickup Inspection Checklist</h1>
<div class="tldr"><p><strong>TL;DR:</strong> Every item to check and photograph when picking up a rental car to avoid return damage charges.</p></div>
<h2>Complete Checklist</h2>
<ol>
<li>Open CarShake and start a new scan</li>
<li>Photograph the front bumper and grille</li>
<li>Photograph the hood and windshield</li>
<li>Photograph each side panel (driver and passenger)</li>
<li>Photograph all four wheels and tires</li>
<li>Photograph the rear bumper and trunk</li>
<li>Photograph the interior — seats, dashboard, steering wheel</li>
<li>Note the odometer reading</li>
<li>Document any existing damage with close-up photos</li>
<li>Generate the QR handover receipt</li>
<li>Share the receipt with the other party</li>
<li>Save a copy for your records</li>
</ol>
